<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h4 id="_3-事件绑定指令-v-on" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-事件绑定指令-v-on"><span>3. 事件绑定指令 <code v-pre>v-on/@</code></span></a></h4>
